graph TD
    A[Input: Text Message] --> B[Create Caesar Cipher Wheel Array<br/>a-z]
    B --> C[Generate Random Rotation<br/>Number 0-25]
    C --> D[Rotate Array by<br/>Random Steps]
    D --> E[Store Rotation as Letter<br/>Position in Alphabet]
    E --> F[Encrypt Each Letter<br/>Find in Original, Replace<br/>with Rotated Position]
    F --> G[Generate Random Salt<br/>Length 0-25]
    G --> H[Store Salt Length as Letter<br/>Position in Alphabet]
    H --> I[Add Random Letters to<br/>Beginning of Encrypted Message]
    I --> J[Add Random Letters to<br/>End of Encrypted Message]
    J --> K[Construct Final Array:<br/>Salt_Indicator + Encrypted_Message + Salt]
    K --> L[Output: Encrypted Message]
    
    style A fill:#e1f5ff
    style L fill:#c8e6c9
    style E fill:#fff9c4
    style H fill:#fff9c4